{
  "texts": [
    "The DeepLIFT importance scores were further used to extract expression-predictive sequence motifs using the Transcription Factor Motif Discovery from the importance scores algorithm (TF-MoDISco) 23.",
    "Here, partitioned sequences, called seqlets, with similar sequence and concordant importance scores were aggregated into contribution weight matrices (CWMs).",
    "The CWMs encoding is analogous to the position weight matrix.",
    "However, despite representing a positional nucleotide frequency, CWMs contain the importance scores of nucleotides associated with the prediction expression classes.",
    "Accordingly, we will refer to CWMs identified with the TF-MoDISco as expression-predictive motifs (EPM) in the following sections."
  ]
}